# Customer Segmentation Project

## Project Overview
This project applies unsupervised machine learning (K-Means Clustering) to segment a customer base into distinct groups based on behavioral attributes (Spending Score) and demographics (Annual Income).

## Strategic Insights Identified
* **Segment 0 (Budget Shoppers):** Low income, low spending behavior. Ideal for discount alerts and value-driven marketing.
* **Segment 1 (Average Shoppers):** Moderate income and spending. Responsive to mainstream loyalty programs.
* **Segment 2 (Premium Shoppers):** High income, high spending power. Primary target for luxury offerings and exclusive VIP rewards.

